INTRODUCTION
============

This module provides access to the MoviePosterDB api.


INSTALLATION
============

   1 perl Makefile.PL
   2 make
   3 make test
   4 make install # as superuser


DEPENDENCIES
============

Class::Accessor
Cache::FileCache
Digest::MD5
File::Spec::Functions
JSON
LWP::UserAgent
URI


